➜Jinshuo Seedling Cultivation Demonstration Base in E China's Fujian Province
http://www.sohu.com/a/418717057_162758	10923
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200916/904c88147ab549fe93c0432dc7e60d75.jpeg" /></p>
<p>Photo taken on Sept 12, 2020 shows the Jinshuo Seedling Cultivation Demonstration Base in Wan'an Town, Jiangle County, east China's Fujian Province. Technological cooperation with Nanjing Forestry University enables the base to master the most advanced "somatic embryogenesis and regeneration" technology of hybrid tulip trees in China, and the ecological benefits of the products are remarkable. The development of high-quality agriculture will drive the masses to get rid of poverty and help to increase income. (Sun Yunqing photo/Guangming Picture)</p>
<p>Photo taken on Sept 12, 2020 shows the Jinshuo Seedling Cultivation Demonstration Base in Wan'an Town, Jiangle County, east China's Fujian Province. Technological cooperation with Nanjing Forestry University enables the base to master the most advanced "somatic embryogenesis and regeneration" technology of hybrid tulip trees in China, and the ecological benefits of the products are remarkable. The development of high-quality agriculture will drive the masses to get rid of poverty and help to increase income. (Sun Yunqing photo/Guangming Picture)</p>
