➜Villagers peeling green walnuts in N China's Hebei Province
http://www.sohu.com/a/418717311_162758	10931
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200916/f414a23edfc7496e9e486cdc3039b40a.jpeg" /></p>
<p>Photo taken on Sept 13 shows that villagers were peeling green walnuts in the yard of a walnut cooperative in Shiqiaotou Village, Dongjiuzhai Town, Zunhua City, north China's Hebei Province. In recent years, relying on the resource advantage of mountainous area, Dongjiuzhai Town vigorously developed plantation of nuts, mainly with walnuts, and adopted the mode of "professional cooperatives+bases+farmers", selling local walnuts to the whole country. (Liu Mancang/Guangming Picture)</p>
